Ask HN: Which math/CS books follow a top-down approach for pedagogy?
text:
Top-down approach:
Instead of building up from the axioms to reach a fact, first, a fact is presented, then it is shown how to use it in practice with examples. Then it is broken down to reveal how and where it comes from. Maybe a proof or something of that sort.

Ask HN: How is everyone electric bill looking like?
text:
Since last year, my electric bill has spiked by over $200 (currently $500/month). This is way bigger than the gas issue, and no one is covering it. I am having to turn on only one monitor at a time to save costs.

I know the summers in Texas have been hot with the Air Conditioners, but this spike is unbelievable.

Ask HN: Which RFCs do you think most developers should read?
text:
Some RFCs are complex and esoteric, and some are approachable educational, and rewarding even for generalists or non-experts.

As an example I felt that RFC 1034 ("DOMAIN NAMES - CONCEPTS AND FACILITIES") [0] was well worth reading.

Which RFCs do you think most developers would benefit from reading through in their entirety (or close to)?

How to download/watch «File no longer available» from Keep2share
text:
The URL of the file page should look as follows ( https://www.k2s.cc/file/examplefile ) right?

If that's the case, simply replace what comes before "examplefile" with ↓

https://api.k2s.cc/v1/files/

and in case there's "referer=https..." somewhere after "examplefile" that needs to be also kept as such

thereafter you'll find yourself on a page which is the source code of the file, so simple look for some link that starts like "https://prx-191.keep2share.cc/video/ random/string/ofnumbersandletters ?temp_url_sig=2f70953eef7d88c2f89cf0b35e47282c508cf53ad6254a8671a8bdea298c9bb8610c1cbe876df0a451a900249eec9c03682820f27190a119e8f31e12fe94d270&temp_url_expires=1620232399&id=0&ip=ignore&node_id=191&countable=1&project=moneyplatform&response_limit=231448342&uf=f3552e0e0ae3e&tags=video%2Cpreview%2Coriginal%2Cwebapi%2Ck2s&name=examplefile.mp4"

Now you find yourself on the video page but the playtime is limited and download can't be finished, so what you do?

You copy the part "random/string/ofnumbersandletters" (without removing it from the URL) and put it without the ".../.../..." before .mp4 replacing "examplefile".

Done! You can use this to download them at the same time, too.

Please upvote so more people can enjoy whatever kind of sick fetish video you can get on keep2share (as if that platform was used for anything else )
